Invocation Name: jungle night sounds
des:
Let the soft sounds of a jungle night lull you right to sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Jungle Night Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
